text: Valéria Frantz-Herpich (1900 - 15 October 1981) was a Hungarian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1900 births Category:1981 deaths Category:Hungarian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Hungary Category:Gymnasts at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pula
